The paper deals with natural language understanding tasks and specifically focuses on Machine Reading Comprehension. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses state of the art models and applies knowledge distillation method, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also aims at improving inference time, which falls under the sub-category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper deals with text data and uses BERT model, which falls under the sub-category of cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
